longBusinessSummary: Quest Water Global, Inc., a water technology company, engages in the construction and distribution of water equipment. It provides solutions that address the shortage of clean drinking water. The company develops AQUAtap, an autonomous and self-contained water purification and distribution system; and WEPS, a water extraction and purification system that produces clean drinking water from humidity in the atmosphere. It serves customers in North America, Latin America, the Caribbean and Africa, the Democratic Republic of the Congo, and Angola. The company was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in North Vancouver, Canada.
